 full-duplex

router bgp 100
 no synchronization
 bgp log-neighbor-changes
 network 91.55.46.248 mask 255.255.255.252
 network 91.55.46.252 mask 255.255.255.252
 neighbor AS100 peer-group
 neighbor AS100 route-map ANN_DENY_2 out
 neighbor 10.0.10.10 remote-as 1100
 neighbor 10.0.10.10 peer-group AS100
 neighbor 10.0.20.2 remote-as 1500
 neighbor 10.0.20.2 peer-group AS100
 neighbor 10.0.240.254 remote-as 500
 neighbor 10.0.240.254 send-community
